    "Our approach focuses on recognizing the present state, predicting the next stage of the junction, and evaluating if the rewards are improving.Our findings show that by identifying a vehicle's current condition, we may predict its likely future state and determine the most efficient subsequent state for the agent, thus improving overall performance."
